OL,3,CBikers rampage in West Belfast
OL,5,FGangs of young people on e-bikes,
OL,6,Fscooters and scramblers ran rampage
OL,7,Fthrough West Belfast at the weekend
OL,8,Fleaving a police officer injured and
OL,9,FPSNI vehicles damaged.
OL,11,FThree men have been arrested over
OL,12,Fincidents arising from the trouble in
OL,13,Fthe Stewartstown Road area on the edge
OL,14,Fof the city on Saturday.
OL,16,FBins and loading cages were placed
OL,17,Facross the road at the junction with
OL,18,FBell Steel Road, with fires being set
OL,19,Ffrom some of those bins.
