OL,3,CBikers rampage in West Belfast
OL,5,FAnd a serious assault involving iron
OL,6,Fbars resulted in a man being taken to
OL,7,Fhospital, with a man in his 20s
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of assault and
OL,9,Fdisorderly behaviour.
OL,11,FSuch anti-social behaviour seems to be
OL,12,Fon the rise right across the city. But
OL,13,Fhow do we tackle it?
